data.description: Welcome to this 2596SQFT, 5-bed, 2.5-bath gem in Sherbrooke Hollow, Meridian. The renovated interior features, vaulted ceilings,  real hardwood floors, newly added kitchen cabinets, lots of storage everywhere, and cozy carpeting in bedrooms. A Oversized 3-car garage, with garage cabinets, and epoxy floors connects to a spacious RV pad with hookups and a generator panel. Freshly painted exterior with brickwork and mature landscaping enhances curb appeal. Comes with two sheds one 8’x14’ and the other is 3’x6’, a water softener, and newly added furnace and water heater, formal dining area or can be used as office, 2 massive 12’x16’ covered patios. Enjoy Idaho living at its finest in this friendly community.
